title: Kristin Shares Why This One Photo Of Her Son Is Making Her Emotional
description:
Baby Jimmy is going to preschool with a little piece of his Grandfather today! Kristin couldn’t help but get emotional seeing her son wearing corduroys made with love out of clothes from her Dad.
